    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Finding yourself out of food, you decide to venture into the outdoors for the first time in an embarrassingly long time in order to satiate your growing hunger.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043280/extras/59c5a27c253c0889717ece923b296b1b.poster.avif?t=1757338032\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043280/extras/59c5a27c253c0889717ece923b296b1b.webm?t=1757338032\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043280/extras/59c5a27c253c0889717ece923b296b1b.mp4?t=1757338032\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Legend of the Corndog(s)</strong> is a First-Person, Open World Experience that <strong><i><u>thrives</u></i></strong> on not taking itself seriously.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Believe us, we're just as shocked as you are.</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043280/extras/f5a1ab823db21a7d7e5804af4161b6d2.poster.avif?t=1757338032\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043280/extras/f5a1ab823db21a7d7e5804af4161b6d2.webm?t=1757338032\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043280/extras/f5a1ab823db21a7d7e5804af4161b6d2.mp4?t=1757338032\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features Include:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <i>Talk to the Locals!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <i><span class=\"bb_strike\">DO NOT</span> Pet the Dog!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <i>Make Shop Vendors lives Miserable!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <i>Experience the pain of a thousand deaths!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <i>Visit Strange Places!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <i>And more we cannot discuss without legal approval!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043280/extras/b0fc0a7dc601d6c88e5669d678be0923.poster.avif?t=1757338032\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043280/extras/b0fc0a7dc601d6c88e5669d678be0923.webm?t=1757338032\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043280/extras/b0fc0a7dc601d6c88e5669d678be0923.mp4?t=1757338032\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
